SYNOPSIS: 
	uwm doesn't redisplay the dimensions box when it is waiting for
you to drag out a window.

DESCRIPTION:
	

REPEAT-BY:
	type "xterm &" at your shell, with no "xterm*geometry"
resource in the database.  When uwm displays the "xterm 0x0" in the
upper left corner of the screen, type "xrefresh".  Notice that where
"xterm 0x0" should be is now blank.

